        Members get exclusive access to our online &amp; hybrid events.
        Tickets to our Annual Conference already include a one-year membership.
      </p>
      <div class="join-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/membership.html#content19-b9">{{ icon("user-plus") }} Become a member</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://billing.stripe.com/p/login/3cscOuaesfHceC4dQQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Manage my membership {{ icon("external-link") }}
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
